megan erin miller arts at stanford university presented by sica home search this site arts enews subscribe about history theme years people contact about sica megan erin miller communications manager sica meganem stanford edu 650 269 3653 www meganerinmiller com megan has been with sica since its inception in 2006 after graduating from stanford in 2006 with a ba in music composition megan drew on her experiences in the student arts community to develop programs and infrastructure to support the arts in student life megan is now communications manager at sica and is also working towards an mfa in web design and new media at the academy of art university in san francisco megan also teaches a course at stanford technology for artists and does freelance work in graphic and web design an avid blogger photographer pianist gardener and cook megan enjoys many creative endeavors and brings that passion and creativity to her work at stanford see all people home calendar gallery news visiting artists grants organizations facilities plan a visit about sica students faculty staff make a gift volunteer login press sitemap contact connect twitter facebook vimeo flickr 2011 stanford university all rights reserved local user login
